our\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Harbour\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We remember quite fondly both freckled-faced Ariarne and her little sister Mia playing in the pool at their family home in Riverside while we the responsible adults enjoyed great barbecues.\\\"\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 927, \"end\": 936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riverside_International_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.8166961854894671, \"rank\": 0.2244439484509384, \"text\": \"Riverside\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riverside_International_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riverside_International_Raceway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Douglas paid tribute to Titmus' parents Steve and Robyn, who relocated their family from Riverside to Brisbane in 2015 to support their eldest daughter's swimming career.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 999, \"end\": 1006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Harbour\", \"score\": 0.9851391662188662, \"rank\": 0.011164032949844596, \"text\": \"Douglas\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Harbour\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Harbour\"}, {\"begin\": 1023, \"end\": 1029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}, {\"begin\": 1049, \"end\": 1054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robyn\", \"score\": 0.9999999781780391, \"rank\": 2.067371355320686e-08, \"text\": \"Robyn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robyn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robyn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nine years on, theformer St Patrick's College studenthas become one of the country's most decorated athletes.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1199, \"end\": 1206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patrick_Star\", \"score\": 0.795263128453366, \"rank\": 0.25743512874203156, \"text\": \"Patrick\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patrick_Star\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patrick_Star\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is heavily favoured to add to her impressive Olympic medal collection (two gold, a silver and bronze from Tokyo 2021) during the next week.\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1392, \"end\": 1397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.5922879888361124, \"rank\": 0.6883653873338085, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What I love about this kid is that there are no airs or graces with her, what you see is what you get, a determined but wholesome individual,\\\" Mr Douglas said.\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1574, \"end\": 1581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Harbour\", \"score\": 0.9851391662188662, \"rank\": 0.011164032949844596, \"text\": \"Douglas\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Harbour\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Harbour\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"No doubt post swimming, a huge future on the speaking circuit as well as commentating swimming at all levels is imminent.\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knowTasmania will get behindthis incredible individual as she strives for gold.\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1795, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Go Arnie!\\\"\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1806, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Titm